# Module Catalog & Reference

Companion to `borehole-platform-architecture.mdc` (always-on boundaries). Load when editing engine, UI, ops, or CLI modules.

## Tech Stack

- Python 3.12 (pinned in `runtime.txt` and `Dockerfile`; 3.11+ compatible)
- **Math/geometry:** Pandas, NumPy, Shapely (polygons/clipping)
- **UI:** Streamlit (internal/external testing)
- **Visualization:** Matplotlib (SVG/vector export)
- **Ingestion:** Config-driven import profiles (`data/import_profiles/*.json`), pyproj for CRS transforms

